sentence.text: Our present study confirmed radiation can promote the in vitro migration and invasion of triple negative breast cancer (TNBC) cells and increase the expression of epithelial-mesenchymal transition (EMT) related transcription factor negative regulation of transcription by RNA polymerase II, while had no effect on negative regulation of transcription by RNA polymerase II, Slug or Twist.
